{
  "stem": "20710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we start walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got blisters.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got-- you know, I didn't have to take off my shoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, my feet were completely, you know, sore, and with blisters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we came to-- [SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We came to the road and then we start stopping some of the-- of the farmers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were going, you know, with the wagons and this, to give us a little bit a ride.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were telling them that we are going to-- we want to go to-- to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they gave us little rides, you know, as far they used to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we begged somebody else to give us a little ride until we came to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We sold this bread and then we-- we didn't have where to go to-- to sleep.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then we-- I mean, we found out that there is a-- a building that they made available for whoever is left and-- and comes in to-- to Lwow, to have someplace to go in, to sleep through a night.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, if anybody's looking for somebody that we can, you know, find whoever's left, that we can find each other.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, I have this-- one of my uncles lived in Lemberg, in-- in a very beautiful area, and this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I went there, there was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I thought maybe one of his daughters, or-- there was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was killed right away, my uncle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But anyhow, his wife and his daughters, I didn't find them.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
